StoredProcedureSqlServerv2k5.name: [sp_GetProjectedGradDateHistory]
StoredProcedureSqlServerv2k5.body:
@NWAID int AS
SELECT H.PROJECTED_GRAD_DATE_HISTORY_ID, H.NWA_ID, CONVERT(CHAR(11), H.PROJECTED_GRAD_DATE, 106) AS PROJECTED_GRAD_DATE, CONVERT(CHAR(11), H.PROJECTED_GRAD_DATE_CHANGED_DATE, 106) AS PROJECTED_GRAD_DATE_CHANGED_DATE FROM PROJECTED_GRAD_DATE_HISTORY H WHERE H.NWA_ID = @NWAID
